snippet.textDisplay: @SupraDarky Can't blame you for skipping IV, really. The gameplay is sluggish compared to the previous ones. III is my favorite, followed very very closely by 2. There's no beating the gameplay in 2, but there's a whole lot of content in III that kept me playing for quite some time. IV just didn't compare in that regard. Nice graphics and it's nice that they added online play, (enough replayability for some people in that fact alone,) but I don't like that they sacrificed that for offline stuff.
